[00:31:58.049] Browser LOG     {"content":"Your support helps New Purpose House provide safe, structured housing and life-changing support services for women rebuilding their lives after incarceration, treatment, or unstable living situations. Through your generosity, we are able to offer women a stable environment, life-skills development, employment readiness, and the support they need to create a new path forward.\n\nEvery contribution helps provide essential resources such as housing support, transportation, job readiness programs, personal development workshops, and recovery support services that empower women to build stable and independent futures. \n\nNew Purpose House believes that a past does not disqualify a future, and your support helps make that transformation possible.","title":"Make a Donation"}
